<span id="freeTextContainer9466136099267436042"><i>The Risk Pool</i> is a thirty-year journey through the lives of Sam Hall, a small-town gambling hellraiser, and his watchful, introspective son Ned. When Ned&apos;s mother Jenny suffers a breakdown and retreats from her husband&apos;s carelessness into a dream world, Ned becomes part of his father&apos;s seedy nocturnal world, touring the town&apos;s bars and pool halls, struggling to win Sam&apos;s a</span>
  <span id="freeText9466136099267436042" style="display:none"><i>The Risk Pool</i> is a thirty-year journey through the lives of Sam Hall, a small-town gambling hellraiser, and his watchful, introspective son Ned. When Ned's mother Jenny suffers a breakdown and retreats from her husband's carelessness into a dream world, Ned becomes part of his father's seedy nocturnal world, touring the town's bars and pool halls, struggling to win Sam's affections while avoiding his sins.</span>
